high_descs: Turn left and go straight towards the wall. Then, hang left and walk straight into the room and turn to the counter top on your right
Pick up bread from the counter top
Turn around and make a straight turn before proceeding to turn left towards the fridge
Place bread inside the fridge and then take it out
Turn around and head straight, then proceed to turn left towards the side table
Place bread on the side table
anns.task_desc: Place bread inside fridge and placing it in side table

high_descs: Turn right, and left, move straight towards the kitchen counter top.
Take the bread from the counter top.
Turn around, turn left, look at the fridge.
Open the fridge, put the bread inside it, close the fridge, wait, open the fridge, take back the bread, close the fridge.
Turn around, walk straight, and right towards the side table.
Put the bread on the side table.
anns.task_desc: To get the bread from counter top, cool it in fridge, put it on the side table.
